   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Nepal Earthquake Reconstruction: Radio and Outreach &#x2013; phase 2</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project produces reconstruction radio programme Milijuli Nepali (Together Nepal)  and supports local radio stations to produce their own reconstruction programmes. This supports the post-earthquake rebuilding process in Nepal, ensuring communities have the information and understanding they need in order to rebuild safer homes and public buildings and increase their long term resilience.</narrative>
